title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: A colleague or friend may voice a drastically different opinion of you than you have of yourself. Their unsolicited perception likely catches you by surprise now, irrespective whether its positive or negative. But dont reject their feedback immediately. Its always healthy to probe the recesses of your psyche for truthfulness. However, projection is the theme of the day. Of course, others might see themselves in you rather than view you clearly. Nevertheless, it could be you who ends up looking at yourself through their eyes. Proceed at your own risk; transparency can be an illusion. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
